      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im a designer working on a new streetwear line. i want to make sure it feels authentic to actual urban culture and doesnt come off as just some tacky cultural appropriation. can u help me define what the actual aesthetic of urban style is so i dont mess it up?",
